<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Installation Successful - Slack Markdown Viewer</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2da44e 0%, #238636 100%);
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 48px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      max-width: 480px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .success-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      background: #dafbe1;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
    }
    .success-icon svg {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      color: #2da44e;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #24292f;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .team-name {
      color: #2da44e;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .description {
      color: #57606a;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .next-steps {
      text-align: left;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #f6f8fa;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .next-steps h3 {
      color: #24292f;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .next-steps ol {
      color: #57606a;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .next-steps li {
      padding: 8px 0;
    }
    .next-steps code {
      background: #e6e8eb;
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .slack-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      background: #4A154B;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(74, 21, 75, 0.3);
    }
    .slack-button:hover {
      background: #611f69;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(74, 21, 75, 0.4);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="success-icon">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h1>Installation Successful!</h1>
    <p class="description">
      Slack Markdown Viewer has been installed to <span class="team-name"><%= teamName %></span>.
    </p>

    <div class="next-steps">
      <h3>Next Steps</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>Go to any Slack channel in your workspace</li>
        <li>Invite the bot by typing <code>/invite @Markdown Viewer</code> or by adding the bot in channel settings</li>
        <li>Upload a <code>.md</code> file to the channel</li>
        <li>The bot will automatically render it and post a view link!</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <a href="https://slack.com/app_redirect?app=<%= appId %>&team=<%= teamId %>" class="slack-button">
      Open Slack
    </a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
